The Leadership Of Baringo County Has Welcomed The Move By A Chinese Company To Set Up An Industry That Will Be Mining Diatomite Deposits In Tiaty Constituency, Baringo. The Move Is Aimed At Bringing Peace In The Region That Has Been Prone To Conflicts Due To The Fight Of Resources In The Area. The Chinese Company Is Set Top Start The Process Of Mining Diatomite In Chepkesin,Kapturo,Katikit And Kositei Areas Eraly Next Year